{
  "stem": "4764.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The village always used to have a main square, like the-- like the village square, I suppose, which it was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I actually went to that square many years later, when I went back to try and find the house where I lived in.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was one family who had a child about the same age as-- as me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think his name was Adam.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were roughly about my age, also a one-child family-- one son.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think they lived in the-- very nearby.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't remember playing with him, but I remember escaping with him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But not playing with him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They did, I-- I remember they did.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They tried, anyway.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they did light Friday night candles.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think they prayed, sort of surreptitiously, in a way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They hid when they were praying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't remember any.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were no presents.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't remember any birthdays.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only this 16-year-old girl who lived with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But nobody else.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I'm not sure whether a child has-- thinks that way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know what a child thinks at that age.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I certainly didn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't remember having any hope, as such.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm not sure whether this is a normal reaction of any child to any situation, but I think-- there was no joy in any of this.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can't remember any happy times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, if you ask a child, does he remember-- does he or she remember certain things or certain-- I think they do remember some of the good times.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I honestly can't remember anything apart from the-- the only things that-- as you're asking me, do I remember anything that was happy, I can't.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the only things I can remember is the traumatic things.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
